igure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-1080x770.jpg\" alt=\"Wildlife Tourism orca\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"321\" alt=\"Wildlife Tourism orca\" class=\"wp-image-71368 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-1080x770.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-800x570.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-450x321.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-163x116.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-252x180.jpg 252w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-768x548.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-1024x730.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-1440x1027.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-600x428.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/17180437\/wildlife-tourism-13-1080x770.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li><strong>Animals can get into a depression<\/strong><br>Did you know that Tarsiers (found in the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/philippines\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Philippines<\/a>) commit suicide in captivity? Primates are very intelligent creatures and are at risk of boredom in environments outside of their wild habitat. This can cause them to have mental health problems, and even go as far as self-mutilation.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5.jpg\" alt=\"wild life tourism philippines Tarsiers\"><\/noscript><img width=\"277\" height=\"338\" alt=\"wild life tourism philippines Tarsiers\" class=\"wp-image-71064 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1572px) 100vw, 1572px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5.jpg 1572w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-491x600.jpg 491w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-663x810.jpg 663w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-277x338.jpg 277w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-25x30.jpg 25w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-133x163.jpg 133w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-147x180.jpg 147w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-629x768.jpg 629w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-838x1024.jpg 838w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-884x1080.jpg 884w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-1179x1440.jpg 1179w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-300x366.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-600x733.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5-25x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193433\/wildlife-tourism-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Alternatives to Wildlife Tourism for Zoos &amp; Aquariums<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of visiting a zoo, consider visiting an ethical wildlife sanctuary instead. Make sure to do your research well, though, through a platform like the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sanctuaryfederation.org\/find-a-sanctuary\/#usa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Global Federation of Wildlife Sanctuaries<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"snorkeling traveling\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"snorkeling traveling\" data-id=\"71448\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=71448\" class=\"wp-image-71448 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18033443\/wildlife-tourism-22-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, htt