strong>Discover:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/national-parks-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best national parks in Sri Lanka to see wildlife<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-558x810.jpg\" alt=\"baby elephant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"233\" height=\"338\" alt=\"baby elephant\" data-id=\"71463\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=71463\" class=\"wp-image-71463 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-558x810.jpg 558w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-413x600.jpg 413w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-233x338.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-112x163.jpg 112w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-124x180.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-529x768.jpg 529w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-706x1024.jpg 706w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18034857\/wildlife-tourism-26-744