e-tourism-29-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-600x776.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18184540\/wildlife-tourism-29.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Donkey Rides<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever arrived at a tourist destination and seen donkeys carrying tourists up the hill as in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/santorini\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Santorini, Greece<\/a>? The owners often tie up the donkeys in extremely hot conditions, without water, and hit them in order to move or go faster.  What&#x2019;s more, they are often cared for badly and made for riding with a badly fitting saddle. This can cause horrible sores all over the body.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2.jpg\" alt=\"wildlife tourism donkey\"><\/noscript><img width=\"230\" height=\"338\" alt=\"wildlife tourism donkey\" class=\"wp-image-71057 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1306px) 100vw, 1306px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2.jpg 1306w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-408x600.jpg 408w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-551x810.jpg 551w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-230x338.jpg 230w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-111x163.jpg 111w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-122x180.jpg 122w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-522x768.jpg 522w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-697x1024.jpg 697w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-2-735x1080.jpg 735w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/15193355\/wildlife-tourism-