/wildlife-tourism-11.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Alternatives to Riding Animals<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If the animal-riding activity is purely for pleasure, it&#x2019;s better to walk with the animal instead or go and see them from a distance. However, animal-riding as transportation can be replaced by walking or taking public transport to your destination. Always remember that: The less money we put into funding this kind of tourism, the more likely it will come to an end. If you want to experience being around these animals, go on an ethical safari in the wild or visit a reputable donkey sanctuary. Always do your research and raise awareness when you do see animal rides taking place.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"safari sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"safari sri lanka\" data-id=\"71468\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=71468\" class=\"wp-image-71468 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18035530\/wildlife-tourism-28-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\